        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "being made free",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") It will be of use to have this connected view of the plan of the apostle, up to the point which it has now reached:—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
